Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:01:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Manabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:01:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Manabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,'Sup?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's this new ramen place by the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go check it out, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've heard those frauds make their so-called "miso butter ramen" with margarine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's just wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Manabe's totally back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a relief, Moritani?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, think this might be your chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! There's no one to get in the way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been a week since Kotoura vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Life goes on, completely unchanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,514)\i1}It's just as if the girl named Kotoura Haruka
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}had never been.
