Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The number you have dialed is not currently in service.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a care in the world, eh, Manabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, so close, yet so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know, you might as well come a tiny bit closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even be bothered to move your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. Just come along to the club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need to participate in the club anymore, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just part of the Kotoura Bundle Pack for you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth and {\i1}come on{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey hey—whoa! That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Stairs! Stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So grit your teeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, hadn't you already recovered?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, until {\i1}she{\i0} came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Man up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly. I misjudged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't believe you'd give up on Kotoura so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Her apartment was stripped bare,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't reach her cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even the teachers can tell me where she moved or transferred.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I really tried my best, but I just can't keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, I've got nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so pathetic, it's actually funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even have a single picture of us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there really nothing left?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Not all the things we leave behind are tangible, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, for crying out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be asking yourself that question!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Manabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She walked into my life without warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We were together for all too short a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the end, she left me with something truly incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,my blazing rage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare that little vixen just up and leave me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find her if it kills me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and I {\i1}will{\i0} give her the soundest spanking of her life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a funny guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well said, Manabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The very words I was waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We, the ESP Society, shall sortie forth
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to retrieve our lost Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, retrieve her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already worked out where she's most likely hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why so surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I simply took a little peek at some data from train station security cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've all but pinned down Kotoura's escape route.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, isn't that a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Forget I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, this weekend's ESP Society activity will be field work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew. It really took forever to get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun's already going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is totally dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Kotoura really here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt that this station was her final stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left is—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's p-pretty cold for May.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been wondering for a while:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why exactly didn't you bring a jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When we set out, I was kind of counting on the flame of my passion to keep me warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask a stupid question...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We start asking around to see if we can deduce Kotoura's location.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately this isn't a big town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone must have seen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Then let's rest up for tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and begin gathering info first thing tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Establishing a command post comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So where are we staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Where {\i1}are{\i0} we staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't make any reservations?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that was {\i1}your{\i0} job!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A heck of a vice-president {\i1}you{\i0} are, Muroto, always screwing up right when it counts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Says the {\i1}president{\i0}! The club's your responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah, guys, chill out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You kids have no place to stay tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, we're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you believe this temple will let us crash for the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Pure dumb luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, Muroto, do your job!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The station attendant told me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't offer much, but you're welcome to what I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,At last I can take a breather.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We were swaying back and forth on that train all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both being rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness no. Please do make yourselves at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So tell me, what brought you three out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of a club field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What kind of club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A secret society dedicated to proving the existence of psychic powers, and to protecting those who have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The ESP Research Society!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,ESP, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh boy do I love that kinda stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hail, fellow fanatic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we swap supernatural stories 'til sunup?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Abso-friggin'-lutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-ho! You'll get no sleep tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a reason why I took an interest in strange phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,About ten years ago, I met a certain little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Something evil has possessed my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, can't you exorcise it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, check this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are all these texts about the occult?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl's strange power was bringing her great pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to help her if I could,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but once I started collecting books I couldn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl with a power that brought her pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What on Earth is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,At what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka, it isn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't blame yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But sir, how can I get my parents and my friends to stay with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I get them to give me a smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do anything for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I feel better now. After all, you're her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she always shouldering everything herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Tell me where Kotoura is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised I'd stay with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That no matter what happened, I wouldn't leave her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And so help me, I {\i1}will{\i0} keep that promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Her family's home is on the other side of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you the way tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka, it looks like you found some truly good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away this time, Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, we strike from behind and take her down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The capture net is prepped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's practice until bathtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:04.22,Alt,,0,0,0,,Truly... good... friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Once she's caught, let me tie her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. Have you found a new school for me yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A new school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to force yourself to go, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I should at least do that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm causing you enough trouble as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'm looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to impose on you for so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You not only find me new schools,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you take care of all my rent and other living expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry your head about all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just come sit on your grandpa's lap once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, dear granddaughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm in high school now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget things so easily these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I looking for... a school...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I could feel my granddaughter's gentle touch,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I might be able to remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You really have grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, Grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, the transcendent touch of my granddaughter's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The spoils of a long life are mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you actually cackling out loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You ought to know that I can hear your thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, you're just like Manabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another despicably fortunate man capable of imagining you like this? What is this blasphemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Grandfather, just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My granddaughter's ass and thighs are {\i1}mine{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All mine! No other man shall touch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:58.54,Alt,,0,0,0,,Actually, you filthy old lecher, they're {\i1}mine{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:12:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hardly believe there's actually a house here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even see any buildings from the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How big {\i1}is{\i0} this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess she really is stinking rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,These are precisely the kind of environs in which we're likely to find a Kotoura or two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she, a cockroach?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Her grandfather says he'll see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But he seems to know you somehow, Manabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,His exact words were, "Manabe's here?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Zenzou, these are the friends of Haruka I told you about last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Looks like they made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he mad at us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and apologize, Manabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you assume it's my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So you are this "Manabe"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask you straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly how have you been \Nmolesting my granddaughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,By making her the star of all my lustful fantasies, and getting off on her embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still quite the novice, aren't you, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, I experienced direct contact with her ass and thighs only just this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well {\i1}I {\i0}think there's a far more subtle pleasure in a face flushed with shame than in crass physical groping!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so your aesthetic tastes are so refined you don't even care
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to feel for yourself the shape\N of her tiny little breasts?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather, I heard the head priest was... here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting bunch of kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem to be enjoying themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why? Why are they all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}Waaait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm scared! I'm so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Damnit, she gave us the slip!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in trouble. This house is too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to split up to hunt her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Why are you hiding from us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry. I abandoned everything and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I'm too ashamed even to face you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But what a relief. You look well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your injuries have healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd like to come out and talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I'm sure you'd just get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kotoura, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why? It was my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't... I couldn't protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You did more than I ever deserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I promised that I'd stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I'd never leave you no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not about the promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just don't want to be apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to see you, Kotoura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, let's go home. Let's be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Manabe. Manabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mana—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crap. Now I'm getting pissed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:17:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess I'll have to give her a spanking after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A spanking. A spanking! {\i0}A spanking{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the only way to atone for making me worry so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I am not without compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How gently shall I stroke your swollen red buttocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gotchya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how about you explain yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you just disappear like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you got hurt, and it was all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought if I left,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you could go back to your normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault I was attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you already {\i1}are{\i0} my normal life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you're saying you'd die without her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But she was just being so stupid, I had to say {\i1}something{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Please don't spank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}did{\i0} hear me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And after I tried to fool you by being all serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like this whole thing is Haruka's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But could you forgive her anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't had friends in so long
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that she just doesn't know how to interact with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she tried to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it seems I can start the \Nre-enrollment process at your old school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going back! I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I do apologize for leaving without saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:19:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't let anyone else get hurt because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please just let me be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Manabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just show her that noble martyrdom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't move idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If I leave you alone you'll just lock yourself up again
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and wallow in your misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What choice do I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If people get hurt on my account, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Moritani?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here, Manabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be asking you that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want with us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just... just to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a detective track you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Moritani?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My stupid jealousy created this whole mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so blind, I even let Manabe be attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You still didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That was {\i1}your{\i0} fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are too good to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And precisely why would you have someone attack your classmate?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you into that stuff? A little deviant, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up! That's why I'm standing here apologizing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't apologized!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, you apologized to {\i1}her{\i0},\N and then completely ignored me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that how you treat me every day?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Moritani did apologize, over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She just couldn't say it out loud because she didn't have the right words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please{\i0} don't tell him that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's just like she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I apologize to you after what I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,When she left, and you started acting all weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:21:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought if I brought her back, I might be able to tell you I was sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're here, now, and I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, screw it. You're just grossing me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's such an awful person, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely despicable. The most contemptible man alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, how am I the bad guy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't let it bother you, Moritani. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wasn't I the victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.97,0:21:31.81,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1579.2,175.2)\blur0.6\b0\fs60\fnArnold 2.1\bord3.3\3c&HFFFFFF&\1c&HFFFFFF&}Separated
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.97,0:21:31.81,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1579.2,175.2)\b0\fnArnold 2.1\fs60\bord0\blur0.6\shad6\4a&HE4&\c&H693923&}Separated
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's funny. I came for forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How did I wind up leaving in tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty pathetic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So while I'm embarrassing myself, let me say this:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've helped me see myself so much more clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can change now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kotoura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:22:06.26,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}How do you stand again when something trips you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did she come here anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She thanked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.17,0:22:07.68,Default,,0,53,0,,{\an3}Then she said, "I'll see you at school."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoura!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.26,0:22:18.73,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}Can truth be found by thinking about the days to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,With you, and with everyone.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.73,0:22:27.32,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}We all come into this world alone when we are born,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! We're going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Manabe-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.36,0:22:29.45,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Yeah! Yeah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:30.53,Alt,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:28.82,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}and precisely because of that,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.49,0:22:35.37,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}we try to live life with others from then on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.33,0:22:35.41,Default,,0,53,0,,{\an3\i1}I guess I was thinking like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought I could understand people's hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:44.17,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}Back then you taught me the strength to live and the meaning to it all,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.91,0:22:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}just because I could hear their thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.71,0:22:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But people can change.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.75,0:22:47.51,Default,,0,53,0,,{\an3\i1}Something that simple never even occurred to me.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.88,0:22:49.47,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}and I embrace it with all my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.09,0:22:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had turned my back on the world. On myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:56.06,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}So that in all things around us the flower of hope may bloom,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.76,0:22:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was a hopeless coward, trapped in my own misery.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.14,0:23:01.40,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}we start our days together here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.85,0:23:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But now I believe I can change, however slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:07.82,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\fsp-1.5\blur2}We start our days together here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.98,0:23:06.40,Default,,53,0,0,,{\an1\i1}Change myself, and change my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I'm not alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,After all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.95,0:23:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,it looks like we got everything back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.87,0:23:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.12,0:23:21.54,Default,,53,0,0,,{\an1}No matter how little,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:23.75,Default,,53,0,0,,{\an1}things have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ungh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.21,0:23:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi-yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.13,0:23:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Eep!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.76,0:23:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Fwap!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.51,0:23:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.05,0:23:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Fwa-fwap!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? Seeing Kotoura cowering before my spanking is sexier than I can bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's {\i1}seriously{\i0} wrong with you, lecher!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:39.98,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,430)\fscx75\fsp-3\1a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\blur0.6}Episode 5
